            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>n</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> deo <lb n="2"/>Mercurio <lb n="3"/>et Maiae matri <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Servandius <lb n="5"/>Serotinus |(centurio) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>III <expan><abbr>Ital</abbr><ex>icae</ex></expan> et <expan><abbr>Servand</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>Herculanus <expan><abbr>fil</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>ex voto <expan><abbr>posuer</abbr><ex>unt</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibentes</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aeti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Text 1 steht über dem Inschriftenfeld. Seitlich des Inschriftenfeldes Pilaster mit korinthischen Kapitellen. Zahlreiche Ligaturen. Z. 3: ME, VR; Z. 4: ET, EM, AT; Z. 5: ER, VA, ND; Z. 6: ER, TI; Z. 7: ET, ER, VA, ND; Z. 8: HR; Z. 9: ER. (B): Wagner: Text 2 Z. 9: merito.</p>
            </div>
